<div class="title"><span>My FR</span></div>

<div class="info_warning">
  <p>
    On May 11, 2016 FederalRegister.gov experienced database issues that
    affected the creation of new users.
  </p>
  <p>
    If you created an account on May, 11 2016 before 3pm EDT and are seeing
    this message you will need to recreate your account. We apologize for any
    inconvenience.
  </p>
</div>

<div class="signup_bar">
  <h2>Resend confirmation instructions</h2>

  <p>We're sorry your confirmation email has expired. Please enter your email address below to recieve a new one.</p>

  <%= semantic_form_for resource, :as => resource_name, :url => confirmation_path(resource_name), :html => { :method => :post } do |f| %>
    <%= f.inputs do %>
      <%= f.input :email, :as => :email %>
    <% end %>

    <%= f.buttons do %>
      <%= f.commit_button "Resend confirmation instructions" %>
    <% end %>
  <% end %>
</div>
